Definition.WordDefinition: hunky-dory adj : being satisfactory or in satisfactory condition; "an all-right movie"; "the passengers were shaken up but are all right"; "is everything all right?"; "everything's fine"; "things are okay"; "dinner and the movies had been fine"; "another minute I'd have been fine" [syn: {all right}, {fine}, {ok}, {o.k.}, {okay}]
